<br>
There is just too much opportunity for what you have stated...a high lvl moron stumbling across you as you are winning and ruining it for you...OR...one responding to they cry for help of a youngling.<br>
<br>
  To counter what you offered, I killed 3 of a group of 6 in HighHold Pass 2 days ago, and then another rogue comes to help them.  He is in my lvl range with similar gear.  <br>
<br>
  He chased me to the slopes  of EK and we jousted for about 5-10 minutes.  I got in a few better shots this time, likely to to me having 4 lvls on him, though his gear was better.  I won, but I sent him a &quot;/salute&quot; tell the first chance I got.  We chatted for 10 mins afterward.<br>
<br>
  PVP has good days and bad, but if you want to win all the time, you have to stack the deck, and NOT fight in EC...its like going to the LA riots with money sticking out of your pockets and expecting a &quot;Stand up Fight&quot;.<br>
